{"tid":2335254,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解澳洲嘅煤炭質素咁高? 會令大陸, 唔係自己開採, 要買人哋嘅煤","createTime":"2020-12-21T17:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T10:46:42.000Z","uid":204929,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"5830e417e32c4cb98eaaed83376ba9eac068e8ba","tid":2335254,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T17:25:43.000Z","msg":"淨係知或效能高, 咁就係點解效能高?<br />\n係咪有咩特別嘅物質<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"8c014bc720334ffbb9c06dabd0481d24b1a17f1a","tid":2335254,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T17:27:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"445d8f83efd58242628692b3ccf91ebd577b44f7","tid":2335254,"uid":52962,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"quote":{"pid":"5830e417e32c4cb98eaaed83376ba9eac068e8ba","tid":2335254,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T17:25:43.000Z","msg":"淨係知或效能高, 咁就係點解效能高?<br />\n係咪有咩特別嘅物質<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T17:31:50.000Z","msg":"中国產的煤，高硫（腐蝕性污染物）、高灰質、低熱量<br />\n根本就唔係用嚟發電嘅材料<br />\n用嚟平時燒炭取暖就話可以，但係會造成嚴重霧霾<br />\n<br />\n平時產地九成係來自澳洲，同埋印尼嘅加里曼丹島<br />\n就算香港中電同埋港燈嘅煤都係來自呢兩個地方"},{"pid":"ee9b217925eed5a935e655773e61d913d2717fba","tid":2335254,"uid":205522,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T17:36:24.000Z","msg":"香港養豬成本貴<br />\n大陸養豬成本平"},{"pid":"83ed7a2b7ee390c41a6593988c538d9e19a1fcd2","tid":2335254,"uid":212878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ee9b217925eed5a935e655773e61d913d2717fba","tid":2335254,"uid":205522,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T17:36:24.000Z","msg":"香港養豬成本貴<br />\n大陸養豬成本平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T22:25:29.000Z","msg":"大陸豬又肥又好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最緊係係多 劏極都有"},{"pid":"69f89f004367e68ba69a7ae744ef4d0d0418bc90","tid":2335254,"uid":285910,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"5830e417e32c4cb98eaaed83376ba9eac068e8ba","tid":2335254,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T17:25:43.000Z","msg":"淨係知或效能高, 咁就係點解效能高?<br />\n係咪有咩特別嘅物質<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T22:42:19.000Z","msg":"廣泛咁理解，煤炭可以分成兩種成份：<br />\n<br />\n1）碳元素(C)<br />\n2）其餘雜質 <br />\n<br />\n咁你燒炭，同樣重量嘅煤炭，澳洲啲煤炭多啲碳元素，燒得好啲，所以效能高<br />\n<br />\n所以唔係有咩特別物質，係少雜質。"},{"pid":"b36147641a0b78fd91ec72661cccd05c9610812b","tid":2335254,"uid":365529,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T22:44:25.000Z","msg":"激到大陸佬起核電你地就知錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8e82a38dd40ca81808b1541974dae25db7bbd5","tid":2335254,"uid":62532,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T22:58:23.000Z","msg":"呢個關經濟體系事<br />\n中國係窮國 但同時又係大國 <br />\n北方地區係冬天一直依賴煤發電<br />\n因為平<br />\n轉其他方法成本又好大<br />\n而且中國有好多煤礦<br />\n但隨住用電量大<br />\n煤礦最外層用晒<br />\n愈挖愈深<br />\n愈黎愈危險 隧道愈長 成本又愈黎愈高 <br />\n而且好高污染 睇下而家臨汾市就知<br />\n國家封左好多煤礦<br />\n但需求仍然係度<br />\n私人機構非法採煤 未有保護下<br />\n出現多宗血煤 而靚位通常比人採晒<br />\n非法採煤出黎既產品多數都係呢D比較劣質既煤"},{"pid":"4c3fe290c4c072316e9c1980161493efeab95d6f","tid":2335254,"uid":77968,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b36147641a0b78fd91ec72661cccd05c9610812b","tid":2335254,"uid":365529,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T22:44:25.000Z","msg":"激到大陸佬起核電你地就知錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T23:40:36.000Z","msg":"一早起左唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4fcaf846bcd68f6282a94f6f6748a3f8df884fd","tid":2335254,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T23:49:27.000Z","msg":"想知媒的高質定低質係受咩影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如歷史上溫度，植物種類，濕度之類有無影響"},{"pid":"064ce1a31fa7eb6e