/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e965c9a7df57dd2883865191ce9df77051197e02","tid":2335254,"uid":44171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T00:57:11.000Z","msg":"支煤都可以用洗煤去硫同雜質，但成本會高好多支那人賺到盡既心態無人會去做。<br />\n<br />\n早十年前左右，山東直頭爆過單係火車站直接拐D民工去礦場做奴隸，仲會捉D女人俾奴隸做性奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事件最後又係不了了之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4aadafbb6dbcd6d0d601fa737330bd0925e5d6","tid":2335254,"uid":57862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:00:01.000Z","msg":"用個乜鳩人造太陽發電啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5b1ba81da24c0375d9dbe734ec57e61f7516d7","tid":2335254,"uid":198175,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:17:22.000Z","msg":"燒煤係一噸煤可以釋放幾多熱量去計價錢,&nbsp;同一時間內燒出嘅熱量越高,&nbsp;就越高質同越值錢<br />\n<br />\n一間發電廠嘅燃燒爐容量有限,&nbsp;同一時間只能燒到幾多噸煤,&nbsp;用cheap煤取代靚煤只會拉低個出熱量,&nbsp;仲會因為要更多時間清爐渣同維護, 結果係間電廠用晒所有爐都無法full cap去發電<br />\n<br />\n支那唔係冇靚煤,&nbsp;不過啱啱改革開放時為咗賺外匯賣咗好多畀日本仔,&nbsp;D靚煤礦差不多挖清光,&nbsp;咁過咗30年到自己要巨量發電時就冇晒靚煤用<br />\n<br />\n咁樓上有巴打提過可以洗煤,&nbsp;不過咁要耗用大量水,&nbsp;仲會整出海量嘅煤屎黑水要倒入河,&nbsp;污染水源vs空氣,&nbsp;結果支共就揀咗保水源"},{"pid":"2963df180e694dac9f1cccaf331ff6a86c7414d0","tid":2335254,"uid":14156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6a24b469fcbc335b5dfd77540805ee1547858aa","tid":2335254,"uid":209738,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T00:08:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TFbZ6j6Cl2I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTFbZ6j6Cl2I&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FSbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=b44dfb8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TFbZ6j6Cl2I</a><br />\n<br />\n從影片（1：35）可見澳洲公司是用機械掘取煤礦，而中國應該還在用人手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:22:50.000Z","msg":"感覺上係完全唔同層次，中國係咪仲挖緊洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b597eb5e967ca3d26cd72f04ff922ecb6d249d64","tid":2335254,"uid":275498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:24:15.000Z","msg":"環境因素<br />\n<br />\n澳洲啲煤質量高好多好多"},{"pid":"95bc6df5753f67b29d5888fede63804f500e1d9b","tid":2335254,"uid":136590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b36147641a0b78fd91ec72661cccd05c9610812b","tid":2335254,"uid":365529,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T22:44:25.000Z","msg":"激到大陸佬起核電你地就知錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://memepedia.ru/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/photo_2019-06-05_13-46-00-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmemepedia.ru%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2Fphoto_2019-06-05_13-46-00-3.jpg&h=c93ae21e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85468938be9377aa47687d6402e9342f545e58f8","tid":2335254,"uid":53705,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:37:26.000Z","msg":"其實成件事都好on9<br />\n<br />\n本身 澳洲軍人 係阿富汗殺平民<br />\n照道理根本唔關中共事<br />\n<br />\n中共外交部 又唔知做乜放張假圖上去, 即係澳洲軍人 割一個少年頸果陣<br />\n跟住澳洲叫中共道歉...........中共唔肯道歉, 而且仲將件事越搞越大<br />\n家陣搞到澳洲 禁止賣煤比中共<br />\n<br />\n仲痴線過 陳同佳事件"}]}